                    <p align="center">&nbsp; <span class="Ueberschrift">Johann
                        Strauss Sohn</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>
          Komponist, 1825 - 1899&nbsp;</p></td>
                  <td><a href="32A_Schubert_28.htm"><img border="0" src="../../Index/B_index/a_pfeil_re.gif" width="60" height="60"></a></td>
                </tr>
              </table>
